   ｰｱｲﾛﾛﾛﾛﾛﾛﾟ ﾜﾟ  ﾟｲﾟ     Release notes:
        ﾜﾜﾜ
        ﾛﾛﾛ   How does an organization know that its cyber security
        ﾛﾛﾛ   controls are effective? In this executive briefing,
        ﾛﾛﾛ   Penetration Testing with Red, Blue, and Purple Teams:
        ﾛﾛﾛ   Executive Briefing, you will learn foundational knowledge
        ﾛﾛﾛ   about active assurance. First, you will learn about
        ﾛﾛﾛ   penetration testing. Next, you will discover bug bounties.
        ﾛﾛﾛ   Finally, you will explore how to make sure the organization
        ﾛﾛﾛ   really learns from a red team exercise and what you can do
        ﾛﾛﾛ   to make sure that a red teams doesn稚 demotivate your
        ﾛﾛﾛ   internal (blue) team. When you are finished with this
        ﾛﾛﾛ   executive briefing, you will have the knowledge of active
        ﾛﾛﾛ   assurance needed to work with technologists, defenders, and
        ﾛﾛﾛ   assurance professionals.
        ﾛﾛﾛ   
        ﾛﾛﾛ   
        ﾛﾛﾛ   More info: 
        ﾛﾛﾛ   https://www.pluralsight.com     
        ﾛﾛﾛ   
        ﾛﾛﾛ   Install notes:
        ﾛﾛﾛ	
        ﾛﾛﾛ   Unrar, Learn and Enjoy!
